description: AMC was stuck with their 290ci small-block V8 for their first season of Trans-Am, making them 100 horsepower down from their competition, due to not having enough time to develop an engine to fit Trans-Am's 305ci engine-displacment cap. Despite this, they were the only team to finish all twelve SCCA races, never winning a race, but earning eight podium positions and two fourth place finishes.
creator: Johnny
